com.shwy.bestjoy.contacts.backup.pim.vcard

接口 VCardEntryHandler

  • 所有已知实现类:
    VCardEntryCommitter

    public interface VCardEntryHandler

    The interface called by VCardEntryConstructor.

    This class is useful when you don't want to know vCard data in detail. If you want to know it, it would be better to consider using VCardInterpreter.
